values:
Fun little romance last night in Toronto. 
Surprisingly feeling a little heart-sick today, though.

Oh, I just spent a month in London. I kept a written journal. Maybe I'll write in this thing. Maybe not.

Google the lyrics to Paramore's "Misery Business" and Avril Lavigne's "Girlfriend" and that's baaaasically my life in a nutshell right now.
School/Exams are done tomorrow. It's been the most incredible semester of my life. I never imagined I'd find such a balance between fun with friends and studying. Work hard, party hard.

Going home on Saturday to start working two jobs because I leave for my month in London in like 50something days. My brother is going to be home the whole time I am. He's playing the last month of warped tour. Chrissy and I want to follow him for a few shows, it would be fun.

Growing up is really scary, fun and cool. I like it.

<center>Oh My God.






update soon. i promise. </center>

The new AARs video just made me cry.
haha.

I just spent 2 hours doing a "My 2005 in picture form" update and lost it.

yesssssss.

THIS JOURNAL IS FRIENDS ONLY It'd be neat to have this journal unlocked due to the fun nature of lurking... However I'll save the creepy lurking as my own hobby. Comment to be added. Please & Thank you.
